direction: right

저장: "케이스 관리 저장\nPOST /api/qa/data"

READ: "old_cases 추출\n(덮어쓰기 전)"
WRITE: "qa_snapshots 업데이트"
DIFF: "new_cases diff 비교"

저장 -> READ
저장 -> WRITE
READ -> DIFF

CREATED: "case_histories\naction=created\nafter=케이스 전체" {style.fill: "#dcfce7"}
UPDATED: "case_histories\naction=updated\nbefore+after 전체" {style.fill: "#dbeafe"}
DELETED: "case_histories\naction=deleted\nbefore=케이스 전체" {style.fill: "#fee2e2"}

DIFF -> CREATED: 새 ID 추가
DIFF -> UPDATED: 추적 필드 변경
DIFF -> DELETED: 기존 ID 삭제

LOG: case_history.log

CREATED -> LOG
UPDATED -> LOG
DELETED -> LOG
